  "article": {
    "published_at": "2026-04-04T01:50:02.000000Z",
    "id": 2040245478923669500,
    "id_str": "2040245478923669583",
    "title": "我这些年科学上网的姿势",
    "preview_text": "第一阶段：纯机场时代\n刚开始接触科学上网，完全不懂技术，自然是从最省心的机场入手。那个年代机场圈还算繁荣，竞争激烈。\n先后用过这几家：\nrixCloud",
    "cover_url": null,
    "content_state": {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "8lkrj",
          "text": "",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "8o5qt",
          "text": "第一阶段：纯机场时代",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "ctv8r",
          "text": "刚开始接触科学上网，完全不懂技术，自然是从最省心的机场入手。那个年代机场圈还算繁荣，竞争激烈。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6jjni",
          "text": "先后用过这几家：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 8,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "cscu4",
          "text": "rixCloud 算是比较早期有品牌意识的机场，界面做得不错，有自己的客户端，当时体验还算可以，算是入门级的\"高端机场\"。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 8,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "aj4r0",
          "text": "Amy（按摩院） 奶昔的分厂，主攻亚太地区。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 2,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "jaaf",
          "text": "奶昔 算是有口碑积累的老牌机场，稳定性在当时口碑不错。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 8,
              "offset": 11,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "ajsih",
          "text": "这个阶段最大的问题是：命运不由自己掌控。机场说跑路就跑路，说被墙就被墙，充了年费结果某天打开订阅就404，这种经历不止一次。加上高峰期晚上 8-11 点那个速度，真是一言难尽。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4r9t3",
          "text": "",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9gmsp",
          "text": "第二阶段：机场 + 自建（初尝试）",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9aj0p",
          "text": "慢慢开始觉得纯依赖机场太被动，于是开始折腾自建。但这个阶段属于\"主力还是机场，自建图个安心备用\"的状态。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "5mqq4",
          "text": "先后试过：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 18,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "eh9vr",
          "text": "搬瓦工（BandwagonHost） 自建的启蒙选择，几乎是那个年代每个折腾VPS的人必经之路。CN2 GIA 线路在当时算是国内访问质量的天花板，延迟低、丢包少。搭 SSR/V2Ray，跑起来那一刻确实有种掌控感。缺点是贵，而且官网买套餐要抢，补货秒没。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 25,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "6ngkt",
          "text": "搬瓦工（BandwagonHost）主要机房和线路",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "b11sl",
          "text": "搬瓦工的核心价值在于线路，机器本身性能一般，选它就是选路由。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 19,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "bkbk4",
          "text": "DC6 / DC9 — CN2 GIA洛杉矶机房，电信走 CN2 GIA 回国，是搬瓦工最经典的线路。CN2 GIA 属于电信的精品网，全程 59.43.x.x 段，优先级最高，晚高峰抗拥塞能力强。缺点是联通、移动走的是普通路由，非电信用户体验打折。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 9,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "5647m",
          "text": "HKBN — 香港香港节点，回程走 CN2 GIA，延迟极低（广州方向约 10ms），但价格贵，且库存长期紧张，难抢。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 11,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "108c",
          "text": "JPOS — 日本大阪走软银（SoftBank）线路回国，对移动用户非常友好，移动有直连软银的海缆，延迟低且稳。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 2,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "feok9",
          "text": "总结：搬瓦工适合电信用户重点考虑 DC6/DC9，移动用户可看 JPOS，联通用户其实搬瓦工并不算最优解。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 4,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "353sv",
          "text": "DMIT 相比搬瓦工更小众一些，胜在线路选择更灵活，有 CN2 GIA、CMIN2 等多种接入，价格稍亲民，社区口碑一直不错，属于懂行的人才会去关注的服务商。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "d8nn7",
          "text": "DMIT 主要机房和线路",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "f90qk",
          "text": "DMIT 比搬瓦工更灵活，同一个机房经常提供多个线路套餐，按需选择空间更大。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 9,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "43ilc",
          "text": "LAX — 洛杉矶提供三个档次：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 4,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "80dko",
          "text": "Lite：普通线路，去程直连，回程走 AS4837（联通骨干），适合预算有限",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 15,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "4nm2n",
          "text": "Standard（原 Pro）：去程 CN2 GIA，回程 CN2 GIA，三网都走精品网，全面均衡",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 11,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "e5lt9",
          "text": "Premium（EB）：去程 CN2 GIA + CMIN2，回程针对三网分别优化，移动走 CMIN2，联通走 4837/CN2，电信走 CN2 GIA，是目前 DMIT 洛杉矶最顶配",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 8,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "7lvut",
          "text": "HKG — 香港",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 7,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "bpfod",
          "text": "Premium：回程走 CN2 GIA，延迟极低，是自建党里香港节点的热门选择",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 4,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "c4g8q",
          "text": "Lite：走普通 BGP，便宜但高峰期表现一般",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 8,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "bn42d",
          "text": "TYO — 东京",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "elf2q",
          "text": "提供 Premium 套餐，回程三网优化，移动直连效果尤其好",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "7rtg",
          "text": "第三阶段：广港专线 / IX / 腾讯 BGP + 落地家宽",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 5,
              "offset": 17,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "2m5m",
          "text": "这个阶段算是质的飞跃，开始认真研究入口和落地这两个维度，而不只是随便找台 VPS 自建了事。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 4,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "cc5ia",
          "text": "广港专线 即广州到香港的专用线路，走的是内地到香港之间的物理专线或优化路由，延迟极低（正常 10ms 以内），稳定性远超公网绕路。对于香港节点来说，这条路是体验天花板。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 29,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "2b94h",
          "text": "IX（Internet Exchange，互联网交换节点） 通过 IXP 对等互联接入，绕过运营商的公网拥塞点，直接在交换层面走高质量路由。理解这一层之后，选节点和选服务商的逻辑就完全不一样了，开始会看 BGP 路由、AS 号这些东西。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 6,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "80se4",
          "text": "腾讯 BGP 利用腾讯云等大厂 BGP 网络作为中转入口，依托大厂对三网（电信/联通/移动）的优化能力，解决了国内不同运营商访问质量不一致的问题。大厂 BGP 的 IP 段本身不容易被墙，稳定性也比普通 VPS 强得多。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 4,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "f3t9g",
          "text": "落地家宽 这是整个链路里最有意思的一环。海外落地从机房 IP 换成住宅 IP（家宽），适合一些特殊场景使用。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 34,
              "offset": 28,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "508js",
          "text": "这个阶段的核心思路已经从\"找一台能用的服务器\"升级成了：精心设计一条完整的链路——国内优质入口 → 中转层 → 海外优质落地，每一段都要单独优化。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9uj06",
          "text": "专线的路由逻辑——到底过不过防火墙？",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9psov",
          "text": "这是很多人容易搞混的地方，理解路由层面的差异，才能真正理解为什么\"专线\"体验不一样。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "c1dd6",
          "text": "普通 VPS 自建的路由路径",
          "type": "ordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "7558q",
          "text": "你的设备 → 国内运营商公网 → GFW 检测 → 海外公网 → 目标服务器",
          "type": "blockquote"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 7,
              "offset": 90,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "1rfav",
          "text": "流量走的是公共互联网，每一个包都要经过 GFW 的检测节点。协议混淆（XTLS、REALITY 等）的作用就是让流量在这一段看起来像正常 HTTPS，降低被识别和干扰的概率。本质上还是在过防火墙，只是尽量\"伪装通过\"。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "d3f5j",
          "text": "2.     IEPL 的路由路径",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 49,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "9h86l",
          "text": "IEPL（International Ethernet Private Line，国际以太网专线） 是运营商之间签订的物理或逻辑专用链路，数据走的是独立于公共互联网的专用通道。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "1fo7h",
          "text": "你的设备 → 国内接入点（专线入口） → IEPL 专用通道 → 海外落地点 → 目标服务器",
          "type": "blockquote"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 11,
              "offset": 5,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "6db8l",
          "text": "关键在于：这条通道不经过 GFW。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3qnhe",
          "text": "GFW 的检测部署在公共互联网出口，而 IEPL 绕过了这些出口节点，走的是运营商间的专用互联链路。所以 IEPL 节点的特点是：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6s5q2",
          "text": "不需要协议混淆，用最简单的 SS 也能稳定跑",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "b5dqr",
          "text": "延迟极低且极稳定，几乎没有晚高峰波动",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "93v59",
          "text": "被封的风险极低，因为 GFW 根本看不到这条链路",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 4,
              "offset": 3,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "9uakk",
          "text": "代价是成本极高，IEPL 带宽按 Mbps 向运营商租用，价格远高于普通 VPS，所以机场卖 IEPL 节点的套餐普遍偏贵，且往往限速或限流量。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "aojfv",
          "text": "3.     IX 的路由路径——与真实 IEPL 的差异",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 29,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "b1hkb",
          "text": "IX（Internet Exchange，互联网交换节点） 在名字和宣传上经常和 IEPL 混用，但路由逻辑有本质区别，需要单独说清楚。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "acl2t",
          "text": "IX 的路径大致是：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "1uqmc",
          "text": "你的设备 → 国内大厂云网 → IXP 交换节点 → 出口落地",
          "type": "blockquote"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "255hb",
          "text": "与 IEPL 的核心差异在于：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 20,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "f0gtl",
          "text": "IX 的国内段只能走国内大厂机器作为入口，通过内网到达IX接入点完成交换，再经过专线落地。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "b7h61",
          "text": "这意味着：",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "fuf7e",
          "text": "国内出境段需要有前置机，前置机与IX入口走云厂内网。",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "t57s",
          "text": "不过墙，意味着你的落地机可以直接用ss协议",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "74gg9",
          "text": "你的带宽上限受限于你的前置机",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2dmkh",
          "text": "你需要单独购买前置机",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9sff7",
          "text": "几个需要注意的点，你的落地机使用什么协议取决于是否过墙。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "69a56",
          "text": "我目前在使用的",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "eog97",
          "text": "1、机场",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4ojl3",
          "text": "仅存eNet一家，不限时的500G流量，完全做备用。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "45mh2",
          "text": "2、线路机",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "bbrvb",
          "text": "DMIT Malibu ，一年$49，三网去回均走电信CN2，每月流量1T(双向)",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "a92rd",
          "text": "DMIT Corona，一年$49，三网各自优化，每月流量2T(双向)",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6ttld",
          "text": "3、专线机",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "10cff",
          "text": "po0 腾讯华东入口，年付1180，200m带宽，每月流量500G(单向)。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "637vm",
          "text": "你可以理解成是包含了前置机的IX，只不过这是满血版的腾讯锐驰套餐的前置机。正常你在腾讯云买的锐驰只是峰值带宽200m，你如果长时间跑，很快就会被限速，而这个不会。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "cm3u7",
          "text": "目前po0为主打方案，入口机直接nftables内核转发到RFC的JPT1和HKT1，相当于同时拥有了沪日专线与沪港专线。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "dbg5e",
          "text": "4、落地家宽",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "43kd2",
          "text": "Boil 家里云，现在基本上没有使用了，注意是港机限制还是有点多，AI不能用。从一个月$9起价，同时还有很多绝版套餐，比如季付297、半年付777等。",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "aqu6t",
          "text": "vircs，AT&T落地，50m带宽，流量不限，$276/年，主要做AI分流、PayPal分流。用DMIT做中转相当丝滑。",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "bc1a0",
          "text": "",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "54n9f",
          "text": "如何看你的vps路由",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "ddi3s",
          "text": "安装nexttrace",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 0,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "7p1mu",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9cfkg",
          "text": "下图是DMIT Malibu回程的路由，可以看到直连无绕路，直接从LA走CN2回国。",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 1,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "a70b2",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        }
      ],
      "entityMap": [
        {
          "key": "0",
          "value": {
